{
  "doc_id": "2802",
  "text": "Chromosome spreads were prepared using standard cytogenetic techniques, DNA was stained with DAPI, and images were obtained using a Zeiss Axioskop 2 Plus microscope. Scoring of chromosome aberrations was performed according to the classification system of Savage [CITATION_1] . Furthermore, all scoring was performed, in which possible, in a blinded manner. For color karyotyping of spontaneous polyploid p53 À/À cells, analysis was performed by Chrombios GmbH (Munich, Germany).",
